next
  Summary: activity record is the single substrate; capture moved to ap_core_broker; mutant tables dropped; warfare shim widened; cross-map social_base_transit
  Gameplay:
    Added: Social Base Transit. Principled stalker squads walk cross-map to a faction base on another level when no same-level base satisfies the same-level Social Base cause. Per-faction destination levels read from gamedata/configs/ap_transit.ltx.
    Added: Transit balance limiter. Per-(level, faction) outflow/inflow counter with 3-game-day window blocks repeated drain of one level and over-fill at another. Persisted across saves.
  News:
    Changed: News composer reads the broker activity record. Standalone ledger retired.
    Changed: PDA marker shows action, consequence, subject (and other if any), target smart with level, and dispatch time. Mutant subjects render as species only.
    Removed: News Chance slider. Compose interval and scope filter remain.
  MCM:
    Added: Causes > Needs > Social Base Transit toggle.
    Added: Consequences > Social Base > Social Base Transit toggle, rush, arrive action.
    Added: Framework > Transit balance cap (1-10) and Transit balance window (1-7 game-days).
    Changed: Per-consequence rate limit slider (consequence_max_events) applies mid-session.
    Renamed: Mutator cfg keys follow mutator_<name>_<setting>. Saved MCM values for the old keys revert to defaults on first load.
  Modder API:
    Added: ap_api.add_record - publish to the activity record.
    Added: ap_api.get_record / get_records - read activity records.
    Changed: Activity record fields are localization keys; translate via ap_api.get_text at render.
  X-Ray & xlibs:
    Added: xlevel.get_level_id_by_name. Lazy name to level_id map from SIMBOARD.smarts_by_names.
    Added: xttltable TTL counter :export / :import for save/load round-trip.
    Added: xttltable token bucket :set_rate(rate). Updates refill rate without rebuilding; preserves in-flight token state.
  Localization:
